    <p>$99</p>
    <p>This slim, el­e­gant smart ceil­ing light works wire­lessly via Wi-Fi, al­low­ing users to con­trol it us­ing the Kyla app (avail­able on An­droid and iOS) from any­where – even out­side the home.</p>
    <p>It is com­pat­i­ble with Google As­sis­tant and Ama­zon Alexa voice as­sis­tants, so users can “tell” the light to switch on or off.</p>

